{"tid":1862743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求起底］又一個賣口罩呃錢嘅仆街 有全名同銀行","createTime":"2020-02-04T19:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T00:19:21.000Z","uid":32171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e96c3eb342cc4d852da4d6b2d602ce7caaf9c919","tid":1862743,"uid":32171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你睇到呢個post唔該盡快搵返我</span><br />\n<br />\n1月26日我見到有條友叫<span style=\"color: red;\">Kan Chiu Ming</span>係Facebook 到賣3m 1860口罩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0X5VwUN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0X5VwUN.png&h=dcba001a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我一開始見佢正正常常咁就同佢講話想要兩盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後佢就叫我入數之後先寄出,佢仲要講到好似真咁話要快啲入數如果唔係嘅話就比下一個（我認我係on9冇cap對話圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n之後到我入完數之後隔咗幾日佢都未寄,我就問佢仲要等幾耐,佢嗰時都答我過多幾日就會寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢一直都冇寄,去到呢幾日仲要成個fb ac del埋(至少我搵佢唔到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後下面係條仆街嘅銀行ac同原本嘅fb<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PapvkSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPapvkSe.jpg&h=69de4931&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQtv5iV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQtv5iV.png&h=379ab7cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"669295c781056c8f03e2958b5c9a8e01a0c34b8a","tid":1862743,"uid":32171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:55:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2069e5a04a7f52175ce68233decc1e741416d1","tid":1862743,"uid":149349,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T19:56:06.000Z","msg":"傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2755e129b247876f34